info.narration:
-> [
{‘Happy Teddy’ is a teddy bear that we all wanted to hug and sleep with when we were young.},
{‘Happy Teddy’ wants to hug children tightly.},
{‘Happy Teddy’ loves the hug. His memories starts from warm hug.},
{Happily born ‘Happy Teddy’ must be happy all the time.}
]

-> [
{‘Happy Teddy’ is depressingly staring at its own worn fur, lost in thought, not moving an inch.},
{Tainted ribbon around the neck of lost in thought is meaninglessly swinging. Name that used to be written on the ribbon has faded and nothing is visible.},
{‘Happy Teddy’ is staring at thin air, not moving an inch. It is actually staring at young girl’s picture, not thin air.},
{Black plastic eye, sewn to the left face of ‘Happy Teddy’ is hanging on thread.}
]

-> [
{Even though it is buzzy around as #0 is working, ‘Happy Teddy’ is staring at the frame, not even giving a glance to elsewhere.},
{Even though it is noisy around, ‘Happy Teddy’ is not turning its head.},
{The frame in front of ‘Happy Teddy’ is its only concern.}
{#0’s work fails to draw attention of ‘Happy Teddy’.}
]

-> [
{#0 ties the torn ribbon neatly during the work.},
{#0 stops the work in between and cleanse of the frame that ‘Happy Teddy’ is staring at.}
{#0 trimming the torn fur of ‘Happy Teddy’ during the work. No response.}
{#0 is trimming thread of ‘Happy Teddy’, but still no responses.}
]

-> [
{‘Happy Teddy’ recalls birthday party of 7 year old. Itself is packed in big and decorated box.},
{‘Happy Teddy’ recalls great vacation with one kid. Its name was ‘Beary’ at the time.},
{‘Happy Teddy’ recalls countless night with the kid. ‘Happy Teddy’ is holding the kid in.}
{‘Happy Teddy’ recalls him, once kid, who have grown tall. Somewhere underneath a wardrobe, ‘Happy Teddy’ is all musty.}
   ]

-> [
{‘Happy Teddy’ draws its arms and drags Dostoevsky to its wide body. While coughing due to suffocation, #0 is struggling.}
]

-> [
{In ‘Happy Teddy’ ‘s hug, #0 is gradually shattered. Longing scent emanates in several places where the fur of ‘Happy Teddy’ fall out. }
{‘Happy Teddy’ is gradually binding #0, tying arms. Movement of #0 slows down. ‘Happy Teddy’ is still not letting #0 go.}    
]

-> [
{#0 is captivated by unexplainable depression. Rest of one’s life is meaningless and is just a mere worthless human being.}   
]

