    {The teddy has shaggy fur and is missing one eye.}
   ]

-> [
   {Around its neck it has a ribbon with what looks like a name written on it. Maybe from a loving old owner. It is too worn out to distinguish the name.}
  ]

-> [
   {Creature’s shoulders are slouched as if it knows that it has been abandoned. It seems to like hugs.}
  ]

